name: 阿努克·达尔文·霍梅伍德
name_full: 阿努克·达尔文·霍梅伍德 Anouk Darwin Homewood
introduction: Anouk Darwin Homewood is a 13 year old fully Bi-lingual English/French actress. She lives in France with her parents and three siblings. Her Grandfather, Step Grandmother, father and siblings are all actors. Anouk can be seen in the upcoming Warner Brothers/New line cinema Horror film 'The Nun 2' which is the 8th film in the series of the hugely successful 'Conjuring' franchise. It is due to be released on September the 8th 2023. Following The Nun'. Anouk secured the role of 'Marie Therese' in Gianluca Jodice's harrowing masterpiece 'Le Deluge' (The flood) A film about the last few months of Marie Antoinette, Louis XVI, and their children's lives, starring Melanie Laurent and Guillaume Canet. 'Le Deluge' will be released later this year.
